eed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1640611288.0142221", "card_id": "Q_506119838", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 90}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年即将结束，你有什么想对自己说的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-802871a17219e1512cacad82d49e6cd9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/506119838"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IxbWDgpGMuLxMEAMaCDc0NzUyNDg2IMH/5I0GMAA4YkAacgk1MDYxMTk4Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1640611288.0146532", "card_id": "Q_508104976", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果将文物中的神兽召唤到现实空间，会发生些什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "无论是欣赏古代建筑遗迹，还是参观博物馆文物陈列，我们都能看到「神兽」的身影。它们生于天地之间，虽形貌怪异，却本领异常，被冠以「神兽」的名号。 大家耳熟能详的就是上古四大神兽：青龙、白虎、朱雀、玄武，个个本领高强，富有神秘色彩。守护东方的青龙，能避邪致富的战伐之神——白虎，古人认为白虎是一种祥瑞，「百兽之长」、「德至鸟兽」；以及神鸟朱雀、龟蛇合体的玄武；它们被古人崇拜，奉为部落图腾。 此外，还有传说中凶恶贪食的饕餮、招财进宝的貔貅、喜烟好坐的狻猊…古人希冀借助「神兽」驱邪避讳，祈求吉祥。我们不妨大胆想象一下，如果可以将文物中的神兽召唤到现实世界里，会发生些什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d763a54703fd482c8fffce13e33c9a8_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/508104976"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IxbWDgpGMuLxMEAMaCDc1MTkzNzcxIKjWlY4GMAA4PkAbcgk1MDgxMDQ5NzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1640611288.0153341", "card_id": "Q_487510346", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 82}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪本书在你的阅读史里可以「封神」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "可以是专业性，可读性，一般人没有读过…任何角度都可以～"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-db919c6409772f9712708c34470474a5_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_col